A cyberpunk cityscape at night with streams of glowing data packets flowing through neon-lit channels between towering server buildings, some packets being diverted through illuminated filter gates that split into different colored pathways - red urgent streams shooting upward, blue grouped streams merging together, and purple special streams taking winding routes, while a few stray particles fall into a dark maintenance chute below, all rendered with rain-slicked surfaces reflecting the electric blues and magentas of holographic advertisements
